{"tid":1747390,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"九巴正仆街","createTime":"2019-11-23T07:49:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-23T23:03:30.000Z","uid":316700,"like":5,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"17b46e85586682356c5b635ad179cb250dff4b24","tid":1747390,"uid":316700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T07:49:45.000Z","msg":"屌你老味狗巴 11月11號之後就喺度玩嘢 <br />\n特登啲車唔入旺角<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SxGGhho.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSxGGhho.png&h=04767a55&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n咁撚驚青唔好做生意啦屌你老母<br />\n搞到我每日要行多10分鐘<br />\n去開旺角油麻地仲衰 <br />\n仲要坐黨鐵去深水埗轉你啲19車<br />\n啲車仲要借啲意唔開 <br />\n咩N368   63X淨係得返下繁轉車站返去洪水橋<br />\n條路都開返啦 人地城巴新巴都入返去賺錢啦<br />\n你就唔撚係嘅 借啲意收車喺度賺錢 <br />\n社會責任去咗邊呀<br />\n上次就仲衰 喺欽州街等車返去<br />\n屌你老味好似玩跳飛機咁 <br />\n一架經欽州街 另一架就唔經<br />\n真係屌你老母狗巴班退休狗高層 冇撚改錯名嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca0f47b66e4f25053998fb6af9c487a0f4144855","tid":1747390,"uid":68445,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T07:51:01.000Z","msg":"個app成日有鬼車 屌佢老味<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n簽名檔：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hcbKZmc.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhcbKZmc.gif&h=5cafa909&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4a4521c7322523df2bf0ca6fb7c28597f24398ff","tid":1747390,"uid":48582,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T07:51:22.000Z","msg":"成條彌敦道得新巴<br />\n冇晒九巴阻撚住晒不知幾爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2a8d2d35b5e24628b5502e734e287d4d58cb97c","tid":1747390,"uid":316700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ca0f47b66e4f25053998fb6af9c487a0f4144855","tid":1747390,"uid":68445,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T07:51:01.000Z","msg":"個app成日有鬼車 屌佢老味<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&md